<node id="Splunk每週onsite">
  <data key="d0">Splunk每週onsite</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Splunk每週onsite, also referred to as weekly on-site maintenance activities conducted for clients such as B客戶, involves regular visits and presence for Splunk-related work. This service is provided specifically for the management and maintenance of B客户的 Splunk system by engineers like A人员 and C人员. Each week, these personnel carry out onsite visits to ensure the system's operational efficiency through various maintenance tasks. The purpose of Splunk每週onsite is to provide consistent support and address any issues or needs that arise with B客户’s Splunk system on a weekly basis.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite refers to weekly on-site maintenance activities conducted by engineers for Splunk systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Splunk每週onsite refers to weekly on-site activities conducted for maintenance purposes.</data>
