<node id="B人員">
  <data key="d0">B人員</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">B人员 is an engineer with multiple responsibilities related to system maintenance. This role involves carrying out maintenance tasks and managing maintenance records for designated clients, particularly C客户. B人员 plays a crucial role in maintaining and documenting the health and performance of systems under their care, ensuring comprehensive support throughout the entire maintenance cycle.

Additionally, descriptions indicate that B人员 is responsible for handling maintenance work for other clients such as D客户. The engineer oversees various processes and tasks to ensure proper system functioning, emphasizing the versatility and broad scope of responsibilities related to system maintenance.

B人员's duties include conducting maintenance work and maintaining records related to these activities. This highlights the comprehensive nature of their role in system upkeep and support, encompassing both practical implementation and documentation tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance work for C客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance work.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer responsible for handling the maintenance tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;B人员is an engineer responsible for maintaining C客户的systems or equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員is the engineer handling the maintenance record for C客戶.</data>
