<node id="Splunk Indexer Queue Full - 20251211">
  <data key="d0">Splunk Indexer Queue Full - 20251211</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Splunk Indexer Queue Full issue refers to a technical problem where the indexer queue exceeded capacity on December 11, 2025.</data>
