<edge source="B客戶" target="A人員">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(A人员, B客户) refers to a relationship where A personnel provide various maintenance and support services to B客户. These services include on-site maintenance for B客户的 systems, addressing any issues that arise as documented in B客户的 maintenance records, and performing regular maintenance tasks as part of an ongoing service process. Specifically, A人员 is responsible for ensuring the proper functioning and upkeep of B客户的 equipment and systems by conducting onsite visits and providing timely assistance to resolve any problems encountered.

The descriptions collectively indicate that A人员 regularly visit B客户's premises to conduct necessary maintenance checks and repairs, adhering to a structured schedule designed to prevent breakdowns and ensure optimal performance. Additionally, A人员 are involved in documenting issues and their resolutions within the context of B客户的 maintenance records, thereby maintaining thorough and up-to-date service histories.

This relationship underscores the collaborative effort between A人员 and B客户 to maintain operational efficiency through continuous support and proactive problem-solving.&lt;SEP&gt;B客户有维护记录，由A人员进行处理。&lt;SEP&gt;A人員performs maintenance activities for B客户的系统.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provided maintenance services for B客戶involving the handling of Splunk system issues and recommendations.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員performs maintenance and support tasks for B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;A人員provides maintenance services for B客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">client engineer interaction,client relationship,customer service,engineer involvement,engineer responsibility,maintenance,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,record,service provider,service provision,support,technical support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-75fa98905e1d68515f390e75c46adddb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04465635a6b88183cbabbfe7e25635dd</data>
