  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="B客戶" target="C人員">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B客户, C人员) refers to a relationship where personnel from organization or role C (C人员) provide various maintenance services and supports for customer or client B (B客户). This relationship encompasses multiple aspects of support activities including conducting maintenance tasks such as resolving issues related to hardware components like IDX hard drive space. C人员 are involved in the ongoing maintenance of systems used by B客户, which includes handling routine maintenance activities and supporting other personnel in their efforts to maintain these systems efficiently.

C人员's responsibilities include maintaining system stability and performance through regular checks and repairs. Their involvement ranges from addressing specific hardware issues to broader support roles aimed at ensuring continuous operational efficiency for B客户的systems. This comprehensive approach ensures that any necessary maintenance is carried out promptly, thereby minimizing downtime and maximizing the effectiveness of B客户的technological infrastructure.

C人员 coordinates maintenance activities for B客户 and provides a range of services during various time periods as documented in maintenance records handled by C人员. Specifically, they address issues related to hardware components like IDX hard drive space and collaborate with other personnel to ensure optimal system performance for their client. In summary, C人员 provide ongoing support through regular activities, issue resolution, and collaboration to maintain B客户的systems effectively.

Throughout the maintenance process, C人员 are consistently involved in addressing and resolving various technical issues to support the continuous operation of B客户的systems. Their work is documented and spans multiple contexts within the maintenance framework provided by their organization or role.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員provided maintenance service for B客戶's system during the specified time period.</data>
  <data key="d9">client relationship,customer relationship,engineer involvement,engineer responsibility,issue resolution,maintenance,maintenance coordination,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,record,service provider,service provision,support</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-daa296a353c26f41dfc613743d24e936&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-72f381579d364fa91cc3e73153e0af97&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-412e17859c430b9ce8b929bc152053ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf168eec40aae386455af5027929f6fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d96ca3133c54d9d76add7de434ee05b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e6e1908b68b82814f06780675f7938b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7504d68fad10caa1cd0ea41314ed2ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3781d1671ca7126e99e7656264965fb6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-39206ec5906f23d68e051b1df74d3ca7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2940790b50eb2cba2a5e944b95a94dd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95280ea367581dac710f0dc56c7a72f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-333af5cc1ff286e512f36be66d1aa78b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f62a98ad02d11a4c9618cbda43281859&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8ebe784b7ece61edcdd2e054763c0ce3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84c3e0271089b72556be831ea38a055f</data>
