  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人员, E客户) represents a professional relationship where C人员 provides various maintenance services to E客户. This includes conducting maintenance activities at E客户的 site and handling the maintenance records for E客户. C人员's role involves both performing and managing maintenance tasks as part of their responsibilities towards E客户. The descriptions emphasize that C人员 provided maintenance services during specific time periods, indicating a consistent engagement in these duties over different occasions. Specifically, C人员 is responsible for providing maintenance support for E客户的 system, including the Splunk system, during specified time periods. Overall, C人员 ensures that all maintenance needs of E客户 are met through proactive service provision and record management, which includes both performing maintenance tasks and conducting support activities as part of their responsibilities.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員负责处理与维护E客户的记录。&lt;SEP&gt;C人员provided maintenance services to E客户involving Splunk 2025 MA.&lt;SEP&gt;Maintenance work for E客戶is conducted by C人員.</data>
