<edge source="C客戶" target="B人員">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(B人员, C客户) refers to a relationship where B人员 provides various maintenance-related services and support to C客户. Specifically, B人员 handles and documents maintenance activities and records for C客户的 systems. This includes providing general maintenance services as well as specific support related to the maintenance of C客户的 systems. B人员 is responsible for ensuring that C客户的 system receives continuous support throughout specified periods, maintaining detailed documentation on all maintenance activities conducted.

B人员 performs a variety of tasks in this capacity, including handling the maintenance record for C客户 and conducting regular checks to ensure the optimal functioning of their systems. The relationship encompasses not only routine maintenance services but also specific support tailored to the unique needs of C客户的 systems. B人员 is tasked with both providing service and carrying out maintenance work as documented in the maintenance records, ensuring that all necessary steps are taken to keep C客户的 system operational and efficient.

Overall, (B人员, C客户) describes a comprehensive relationship where B人员 offers continuous support and maintenance services to C客户 through meticulous documentation and proactive intervention.&lt;SEP&gt;B人員provides maintenance support services for C客戶.</data>
  <data key="d9">client-engineer relationship,customer support,maintenance,maintenance record,maintenance service,maintenance support,maintenance work,service,service provider,service provision,support</data>
